PrecisAuthority to enter into a COMPREHENSIVE LAND CLAIM AGREEMENT with the SAHTU DENE AND METIS peoples in the Northwest Territories which provides for the transfer to those peoples of the ownership of 16,000 square miles of land situated in the Mackenzie Valley region and 136 square miles of land situated in the Deh Cho region, the payment of financial compensation and a share of the royalties on resources.
